:vessel::d5cc4d36-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a09ddc00-35b8-11f0-9e75-4f8a8390a300/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d36-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a09d18b0-35b8-11f0-b634-a5c058b5cf83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d36-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a09f1480-35b8-11f0-b634-a5c058b5cf83/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Itimat Shipyard","model":"","maxCrew":4,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::d51ce592-b3ed-11ed-9373-325096b39f47","name":"Bodrum","coordinates":{"latitude":37.03482562918905,"longitude":27.42932494208488},"country":"Türkiye"},"cruisingCapacity":8,"staticCapacity":0,"builtYear":2013,"architect":"","interiorDesigner":"Alex Banakis","refitYear":2022,"topSpeed":0,"cruiseSpeed":12,"fuelCapacity":0,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Master Cabin","value":"2"},{"label":"Double Cabin","value":"2"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":4,"length":28.4,"beam":6.5,"draft":3.2,"hullType":"Displacement","hullConstruction":"","tonnage":"","superStructure":["Deckhouse"],"engines":"2 x 400hp Man","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Generators","quantity":"2"}],"toys":[{"label":"Paddle Board"},{"label":"Water Ski"},{"label":"Canoe"},{"label":"Kayak"},{"label":"Ringo"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":"Snorkeling Equipment"},{"label":"Swimming Platform"}],"entertainment":["Wi-Fi","LCD TV in Saloon","TV in master cabins","DVD Player","Stereo Music Player"],"tenders":["3.8m Tender with 50 HP engine"]},"crew":[{"name":"MUZEYIR SEMERCI","role":"Captain","bio":"Age: 54\nGender: Male\nNationality: Turkish\n\nCaptain Muzeyir was born in 1970 and he is from Bodrum, Mugla. Muzeyir has over 34 years of experience in the maritime industry.\n\nAfter graduating from the High School, he started to work on maritime industry. He worked as a captain on several yachts for example Feraye for 11 years, Arielle for 9 years, Zefirya and on a French owner special yacht for 6 years.\n\nHe speaks English fluently and intermediate level of French. This season will be his 3rd season on Luja. He loves the sea so much and has a passion of diving."},{"name":"ERDEM TOPALOGLU","role":"Captain","bio":"Age: 37\nGender: Male\nNationality: Turkish\n\nChef Erdem was born in 1988 in Giresun and graduated from the Vocational High School for Industry. With 18 years of experience, Erdem worked in various hotels and taught at Giresun University before entering the maritime sector.\n\nFor the past three years, Erdem has been delighting guests with unique flavors and holds various certifications such as kitchen hygiene, occupational health and safety, mastership, and master instructor certificates.\n\nHe prepares dishes from world cuisines for his guests on board and is a true rally enthusiast who also loves reading books.\n\nThe 2025 season will be his first year on Luja."},{"name":"OLGUN CELIK","role":"Captain","bio":"Age: 39\nGender: Male\nNationality: Turkish\n\nSteward Olgun was born in 1986 in Giresun and graduated from a high school with English as the medium of instruction.\n\nFor the past 6 years, Olgun has been working on yachts and holds a culinary certificate. Therefore, at the beginning of his career, he also worked as a chef in various hotels and restaurants.\n\nHe is fluent in English, also enjoys sports activities and takes pleasure in doing repair and maintenance work.\n\nBelieving in teamwork and always welcoming guests with a warm smile, Olgun is looking forward to his first season on Luja in 2025."},{"name":"EMIRHAN DEREN","role":"Captain","bio":"Age: 18\nGender: Male\nNationality: Turkish\n\nDeckhand Emirhan was born in 2007 in Aydın and graduated from high school. After finishing high school, he worked in various restaurants and started working in the maritime industry three years ago.\n\nHis hobbies include swimming, fishing, and water sports. Emirhan speaks intermediate-level English, enjoys working, and highly values teamwork.\n\n2025 will be his first season on Luja."}],"pricing":{"weekPrici